{"tid":514255,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"爆大冷！版主數 2017 旗艦手機跌價王！LG 不再是首位","createTime":"2017-12-30T11:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T14:52:21.000Z","uid":23677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7a048bb9c68873889d52d9548308ed84177115ad","tid":514255,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T11:17:20.000Z","msg":"早前版主做過統計，發現了一個好出乎意料的現象：三星、HTC 居然不再是機海之王，2017 第一第二都無佢哋份，卻被華為、華碩奪去寶座。咁版主除左想知道，邊個品牌係機海之王，既然 <a href=\"http://ePrice.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FePrice.HK&d=PANdaGv%2FftUdcD9Ayq7HxuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=6d0e6f1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ePrice.HK</a> 有咁好的數據庫喺度，當然可以比較一下更加多有趣嘅資料。就例如，一向都係 LG 被稱作「跌價王」，但今年情況又有沒有被推翻呢？版主就針對各品牌的旗艦手機，利用數據話俾大家知！<br />\n<br />\n在 2017 年推出眾多手機之中，版主發現賣價減幅最多的五部手機，有以下幾部：<br />\n第 1 名：HTC U Ｕltra<br />\n第 2 名：Sony Xperia XZs<br />\n第 3 名：LG G6<br />\n第 4 名：Sony Xperia XZ1<br />\n第 5 名：LG G6+<br />\n<br />\n當然，版主都要戴定頭盔先，肯定會有網友質疑，唔係喎版主，咁有啲手機早上市，咁當然減價自然會多啲啦。理論上都可以咁講，所以以上的數據，只是比較 2017 全年旗艦機整體賣價的差異，如果真的要說減價最快的手機，我看應該是非 Sony Xperia XZ1 莫屬，開賣 3 個月減到 $3998，是目前減價最快的 S835 旗艦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9dn081o3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9dn081o3&h=c3f752c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hnucwq1f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhnucwq1f&h=5e3269a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"566c17d08463ee74cd743cac2b6208d7d0adbd25","tid":514255,"uid":30510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T11:21:58.000Z","msg":"Sony超抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d059189610019a009c590dc22044ebb8e3b9a24b","tid":514255,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"U11先減得平靚正"},{"pid":"5f621ec9e18fcee1a3b341b43ede65c938de4f89","tid":514255,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime